{"tid":1751732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選贏 最多係開始既終結","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T19:17:16.000Z","uid":75701,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"33931fe8d439b1bf4109ce1d401b6b0d5a23836f","tid":1751732,"uid":75701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:00:02.000Z","msg":"係大家慶祝非建制贏既候<br />\n唔好唔記得 有班手足係理大出唔到黎<br />\n我希望大家唔好放棄佢地<br />\n就算理大得返一個人 我地都唔可以放棄佢地<br />\n香港人付出得太多 先換到一個叫做好啲既結果(其實應該叫開始既終結)<br />\n但係贏到區選 唔係代表我地會停<br />\n應承我 無論未來發生咩事都好 點輸點贏都好<br />\n要我地香港人停<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 真係全部做到<br />\n黑警 又真係清算到<br />\n光復到香港 仲要時代革命到<br />\n先停落嚟<br />\n好嘛?"},{"pid":"dd3553fbc558ae35a85c78f5053956cc2eb14337","tid":1751732,"uid":84122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:01:06.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"1c06fcde81b06447a5282a7e32aaff4f044fe0f2","tid":1751732,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a6e764e66e4c35fae3d53195608f2bc0071cbbe","tid":1751732,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d57f737204c23e8f25a5dc45658b8c415909f900","tid":1751732,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477192cc9e6875ed0b889219c426785c929a9446","tid":1751732,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b678881258913907ad039b6d43b064bb4aff2bc7","tid":1751732,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"選舉還未結束 大家快啲將民賤聯賄選的影片tweet出去全世界<br />\n今次選舉正好清洗所有賄選問題 咁以後先有公正的真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9af25b5615ac0c09f8816326bbbc045ff26a060","tid":1751732,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"抗爭仲有好多目標未達成，大家努力"},{"pid":"3387e02a2a3cbc44682b6f48363e786a11ec2210","tid":1751732,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b678881258913907ad039b6d43b064bb4aff2bc7","tid":1751732,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"選舉還未結束 大家快啲將民賤聯賄選的影片tweet出去全世界<br />\n今次選舉正好清洗所有賄選問題 咁以後先有公正的真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"無錯，要比全世界知支共賄選"},{"pid":"62d051b902b57fee25a6bc6f7744f9aa54fe1f49","tid":1751732,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:09:12.000Z","msg":"理大手足請撐住 好好活著 香港人係命運共同體 請記住我哋有共同目標 唔會放棄！"},{"pid":"6d8866c50778ecdb05df4c9dbe8